high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the sink on your right.
Pick up the egg that's to the left of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave that's on your right then turn right to face it.
Cook the egg in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Take a step to your left then a small step backwards.
Put the egg in the garbage to the left of the counter on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved egg in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the egg from the left side of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the right.
Put the egg inside the microwave above the counter, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, walk forward and turn around to face the gray bin on the floor next to the counter.
Place the heated egg inside the gray bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg in a bin.

high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Pick up the egg on the left side of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the right.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Place the egg in the bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg in a garbage bin.
